Detailed Description

A immutable iterator over the boxes in a BoxContainer.

If iterating over an ordered BoxContainer, then iteration will follow the sequence of the BoxId-based ordering of the container. If iterating over an unordered BoxContainer, the sequence of the iteration will be based on how the members of the container were added.
